"ngram\": \"national success\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 783}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 827}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00c2\", \"from\": 828, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"The scoring machine\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 851}, {\"ngram\": \"the place\", \"from\": 880, \"to\": 889}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Tour\", \"from\": 926, \"to\": 940}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 955}, {\"ngram\": \"another performance\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 991}, {\"ngram\": \"a dude\", \"from\": 997, \"to\": 1003}, {\"ngram\": \"the hype\", \"from\": 1036, \"to\": 1044}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A post shared by 3x3 FFBB (@3x3ffbb) \\u00c2 Anand Ariunbold (Mongolia) There are few players who can turn it on when it matters most quite like this Mongolian dude aptly nicknamed 'The Archer'.\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1106, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9998979784677101, \"rank\": 0.00010159993115032197, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 1195, \"end\": 1204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9981633498270961, \"rank\": 0.0009878743060016887, \"text\": \"Mongolian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A post\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"3x3 FFBB\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1073}, {\"ngram\": \"@3x3ffbb\", \"from\": 1075, \"to\": 1083}, {\"ngram\": \"few players\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1135}, {\"ngram\": \"'The Archer\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He struggled in the early stages of the recentFIBA 3x3 Asia Cup 2024before going on a heater in the knockouts to almost single-handedly lift a youthful Mongolia to a bronze medal.\\u00c2 Ariunbold carried the team on his back in the fight for bronze against New Zealand with an incredible 15 points, including 4 twos, to ensure Mongolia reached the podium.\\u00c2 If he continues on his heat check then Mongolia might just emerge victorious in Hong Kong.\\u00c2 A post shared by FIBA3x3 (@fiba3x3) \\u00c2 Karlis Lasmanis/Nauris Miezis (Latvia) While everyone else dreams of Olympic glory, these two Latvian legends have been to the summit after creating history with gold in Tokyo.\\u00c2 These superheroes are best when playing together because they can take turns wearing the cape.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 2002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1393, \"end\": 1401, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9998979784677101, \"rank\": 0.00010159993115032197, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 1494, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.8894503071030402, \"rank\": 0.0966608304985344, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1564, \"end\": 1572, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9998979784677101, \"rank\": 0.00010159993115032197, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 1634, \"end\": 1642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"score\": 0.9998979784677101, \"rank\": 0.00010159993115032197, \"text\": \"Mongolia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mongolia\"}, {\"begin\": 1744, \"end\": 1757