91}, {\"ngram\": \"FIBA3x3\", \"from\": 1702, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"@fiba3x3\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1719}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic glory\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1805}, {\"ngram\": \"the summit\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"history\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1879}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1885, \"to\": 1889}, {\"ngram\": \"Tokyo\", \"from\": 1893, \"to\": 1898}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"These superheroes\", \"from\": 1901, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"turns\", \"from\": 1972, \"to\": 1977}, {\"ngram\": \"the cape\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1994}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They are known as 'Batman' and 'Robin', but each can be the lead hero when needed.\\u00c2 Lasmanis hit the biggest shot in 3x3 history when he won the Olympic gold medal with a huge two, while Miezis has also made numerous clutch buckets to cement his reputation as an assassin.\\u00c2 Move aside Jackie Chan, these Latvians are the baddest action stars in Hong Kong.\\u00c2 If one does not lay the smack down, the other will.\\u00c2 \\u00c2 A post shared by Nauris Miezis (@miezis_n) \\u00c2 Matthias\\u00c2 Linortner (Austria) This Austrian is an absolute walking bucket and capable of causing a typhoon in Hong Kong.\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2309, \"end\": 2317, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\", \"score\": 0.9999999363562913, \"rank\": 6.364374359838091e-08, \"text\": \"Latvians\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\"}, {\"begin\": 2435, \"end\": 2448, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nauris_Miezis\", \"score\": 0.999999996610768, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nauris Miezis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nauris_Miezis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nauris_Miezis\"}, {\"begin\": 2487, \"end\": 2494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9382668374304981, \"rank\": 0.06579488368446894, \"text\": \"Austria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2502, \"end\": 2510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"score\": 0.9999527429206598, \"rank\": 3.691552533644957e-05, \"text\": \"Austrian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria\"}, {\"begin\": 2577, \"end\": 2586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.5773260488734595, \"rank\": 0.7281269592292715, \"text\": \"Hong Kong\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hong_Kong_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Batman\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"'Robin\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"the lead hero\", \"from\": 2059, \"to\": 2072}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 Lasmanis\", \"from\": 2085, \"to\": 2095}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest shot\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2116}, {\"ngram\": \"3x3 history\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic gold medal\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2166}, {\"ngram\": \"Miezis\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2196}, {\"ngram\": \"numerous clutch buckets\", \"from\": 2211, \"to\": 2234}, {\"ngram\": \"his reputation\", \"from\": 2245, \"to\": 2259}, {\"ngram\": \"an assassin\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"Jackie Chan\", \"from\": 2288, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"the baddest action stars\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"Hong Kong\", \"from\": 2348, \"to\": 2357}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 2358, \"to\": 2359}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 2363, \"to\": 2366}, {\"ngram\": \"the smack\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2389}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00c2\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2414}, {\"ngram\": \"A post\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2421}, {\"ngram\": \"a typhoon\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Memo to defenders - do not leave him open because he's one of the best snipers in the business and he rarely misses.\\u00c2 Linortner's shown his shooting prowess on the World Tour, but now it's time for him to shine at the international level as he eyes lifting Austria into their first Olympic Games.\\u00c2 A post shared by La L\\u00c3\\u00adnea de 3 | Basketball (@lalineade3oficial) \\u00c2 Gilles Martin (Switzerland)\\u00c2 For those who do not know, Martin\\u00c2 has more highlights than Ballislife.\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 3059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2846, \"end\": 2853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9382668374304981, \"rank\": 0.06579488368446894, \"text\": \"Austria\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Austria_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2965, \"end\": 2971, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"score\": 0.822971764091228, \"rank\": 0.21507900832642338, \"text\": \"Martin\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Glenn_L._Martin_Company\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Memo\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2592}, {\"ngram\": \"defenders\", \"from\": 2596, \"to\": 2605}, {\"ngram\": \"the best snipers\", \"from\": 2650, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"the business\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2682}, {\"ngram\":